node.text: We've got a very special guest today. @karltowns and I have been very open in our admiration for one another on social media, but today we're opening up about how we got together, and what's kept us strong through hard times. Tag your best friends and your boyfriends in the comments 💕

node.text: This week on Regular-ish, we’re looking into the future, talking about where I see myself in 10 years. Hope you had some fun watching this Q&A series. I loved hearing your Q’s and doing my best to give you honest A’s. Tune in next week for something new and different!

node.text: Let me start by saying, I didn’t know how much work went into creating an app and platform! @frst.place Almost a year of time spent into this, and filming hundreds of workouts over and over to make sure it was optimal and it’s finally all come together. 🥲 Fitness became my crutch through any hard time and I realized how important it was to my well being. I wanted to build a community of real people who go through real things, but wanted to finally put themselves first. You are not alone in this journey!! Thank you to some of you for being very patient… this is just the beginning 🥰 @frst.place

node.text: We are back with @BeautyByMariama to add onto the ponytail from last week by styling my baby hairs. It's a trend, I'm trying to do my part, get over it. How do you style your baby hairs? node.text:
Sheesh, I got this photo sent to me by the @frst.place team and I look back and have to realize I came a long way and it didn’t happen overnight! I can’t even believe I’m posting this but this is really me and this is my journey. Hopefully this can inspire some of you! It all started with a lot of mental and emotional work and the physical came with it. We all start somewhere. 

With that being said, you've signed up for FRSTPLACE but now is the time to really challenge yourself. ⚡️ Yesterday was the most amazing day hearing everyones feedback and getting on the app! For me transformation was a gradual change from the inside out. I want you to experience all that FRSTPLACE represents in mind, body, and spirit.  That's why we are launching our first ever CHALLENGE with FRSTPLACE! 💪 I'm calling this challenge the #jwstartingpoint challenge and it's going to change everything.  All you have to do win is: 
🏁 Complete 1 full guide from the app
 🏁 Tag @frst.place and @jordynwoods in your transformation pic 
🏁 Use the hashtag #jwstartingpoint in your caption so we don't miss it 
🏁 The most impactful transformation over the next 12-weeks will WIN! 

1st place $2500 
2nd place $1500 
3rd place $500 

Don't forget to complete full guide and tag us in your before/after! We dont want to miss your incredible results.

Where my September babies at!?

BIG MOMENT ANNOUNCEMENT: It just got so real. My app is finally here and I cant wait for you all to try it and love it as much as I do! I can now finally reveal it's launch date 

🥁🥁🥁🥁

The @frst.place App will be launching Monday September 6th at 9am PST!

This app is everything you need to feel your best from the inside out. It literally has everything you need including: 
* Home Guides
* Gym Guides
* Over 42 weeks of exercises
* Recipes
* Water Tracker
* And my personal fav an in app journal

So set your clocks 🕰 and put yourself First from next Monday
